{"tid":1950164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Jefferies CFO 死於武肺 終年56歲","createTime":"2020-03-30T07:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T11:16:59.000Z","uid":89046,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e071dd0119d1779c8a7fc7b96a5a8733ba8fbb9a","tid":1950164,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"首位華爾街高管因感染新冠病毒去世<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Wall Street Journal<br />\nLiz Hoffman<br />\n2020年3月30日10:20 CST 更新</span><br />\n<br />\n美國富瑞金融集團(Jefferies)周日表示，該行56歲的首席財務長Peg Broadbent因感染新冠病毒去世。這是已知的第一位死於這種疾病的華爾街高管。目前全球死於這種疾病的人數已經超過3萬。<br />\n<br />\n這家總部位於紐約的投資銀行周日上午宣布Broadbent去世，同時任命該行金融服務部門的首席財務長Teri Gendron為臨時繼任者。<br />\n<br />\n富瑞金融集團首席執行長Rich Handler和總裁Brian Friedman在一份聯合聲明中表示，Broadbent的正派、冷靜和機智一直影響著公司，總是讓事情好轉。聲明稱：「我們會非常想念他的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%9B%A0%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96-11585534806?reflink=share_mobilewebshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2588%25BE%25E8%25A1%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%2596-11585534806%3Freflink%3Dshare_mobilewebshare&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=ae1334f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E9%AB%98%E7%AE%A1%E5%9B%A0%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96-11585534806?reflink=share_mobilewebshare</a>"},{"pid":"efdde616ac4938150e69bee150ca2ced547ea16b","tid":1950164,"uid":298012,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T07:02:50.000Z","msg":"華爾街班大鱷今次識驚未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef420a83d1